surveystatement.statement:
You will be involved in a test to determine whether timbre is perceptible through touch. 
    You will decide which of the 7 instruments is being played, without having heard them beforehand. 
    You will be displayed an isolated page for a total of 81 trials. 
    Press the play button, feel throughout the playback period and make your choice.
